fields.name: The Beginning
fields.description: Life begins in the test world

fields.name: The First Great Code War
fields.description: This is the first time coders used their skills for evil

fields.name: The Second Code War
fields.description: The losers of the first code war seek revenge for their loss

fields.name: The Creation of Codetopia
fields.description: A perfect Utopia is built where all coders can live in relative peace

fields.name: The Last Great Code War

fields.description: The climax of the final code war brought about the destruction of the perfect city

fields.name: The End
fields.description: This is the end of all things in the test world
